<collectingCountry box="[390,501,1610,1634]" name="Colombia" pageId="6" pageNumber="61">Colombia</collectingCountry>
this species is known from only a few specimens from Central Cordillera in Cauca (western slope) and Western Cordillera in Risaralda at 
<quantity box="[765,849,1646,1670]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7399999999999998" pageId="6" pageNumber="61" unit="m" value="2740.0">2740 m</quantity>
above sea level
</paragraph>
